  <h2>Media</h2>
  <p><a href="https://ableplayer.github.io/ableplayer" target="_blank">Able Player</a> - Able Player is a fully accessible cross-browser media player. It uses the HTML5 'audio' or 'video' element for browsers that support them, and (optionally) the JW Player as a fallback for those that don’t (Terrill Thompson - <a href="https://twitter.com/terrillthompson">@terrillthompson</a>).</p><br>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/paypal/accessible-html5-video-player/" target="_blank">PayPal Accessible HTML5 Video Player</a> - A lightweight HTML5 video player which includes support for captions and screen reader accessibility. For details, read the blog post Introducing an Accessible HTML5 Video Player on the PayPal Engineering blog.</p>
